  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Bergwelt is a well deserved member of the 'Small Luxury Hotels of the World'. Caringly run by the Falkner family, the hotel has a ski-in, ski-out location, large spa area, and a special emphasis on good food and wine.</p>
<h2>Ski-in, Ski-out</h2>
<p>Hotel Bergwelt enjoys a commanding position right on the slopes with great views towards the mountains. Just 20 metres outside the hotel you can ski down to the nearest lifts and access the entire <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/obergurgl" target="_blank">Obergurgl</a>-<a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/hochgurgl" target="_blank">Hochgurgl</a> area.</p>
<h2>Panoramic Spa</h2>
<p>The luxurious spa area is split into four sections and extends over three levels. From the panoramic spa area you can enjoy views across the Ötz Valley from the Finnish sauna or steam bath. The family spa permits swimsuits and features an indoor and outdoor seawater pool, whirlpool, bio saunas and infrared cabin.</p>
<h2>Family Friendly </h2>
<p>The hotel's very own kids club is open Sunday to Friday and offers children 3+ years a wide programme of activities including crafts, weekly pizza baking, children's cinema, and little ones' spa treatments. </p>]]></description>
