  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard </strong>Austrian twins are around 25m² and sleep up to three adults. All rooms have bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites Type A3 or A4 </strong>are around 30m² with an Austrian twin bed and lounge area with double sofa bed. These rooms have a balcony, and can sleep up to four.</p>
<p><strong>Two Room Suites Type C1 or C2 </strong>are 30-40m² and have a sliding door that separates the main bedroom and lounge area with single or double sofa beds. These rooms have a west-facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single </strong>rooms are around 20m² with double bed and small seating area.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable / satellite TV</li>
<li>Minibar / fridge</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobes &amp; slippers</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
